OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Products
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.DESCRIPTION: This selector shows all the available products
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HELP: This selector shows all the available products

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Doctype selector for business partner
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HELP: Selector for selecting the type of document by business partner.
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.documentCategory in (case when @inpdocumentcategory@='ORD' and @inpissotrx@='true' then 'SOO' when @inpdocumentcategory@='ORD' and @inpissotrx@='false' then 'POO' when @inpdocumentcategory@='INV' and @inpissotrx@='true' then 'ARI' when @inpdocumentcategory@='INV' and @inpissotrx@='false' then 'API' when @inpdocumentcategory@='SHIP' and @inpissotrx@='true' then 'MMS' else 'MMR'end) and e.active = true and e.client.id = @#AD_Client_ID@ and AD_ISORGINCLUDED(@inpadOrgId@, e.organization.id, e.client.id) <> -1

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Invoice Line Selector
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.DESCRIPTION: Invoice Lines that can be added to a Landed Cost
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HELP: A selector that proposes Invoice Lines that can be linked to a Landed Cost.
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: (e.product.id = @LCC_Product_ID@ or e.account.id = @LCC_Account_ID@) and e.lineNetAmount <> (SELECT coalesce(sum(lcm.amount), 0) from LandedCostMatched lcm where lcm.invoiceLine.id = e.id) and e.invoice.salesTransaction = 'N'

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Legal or Business Organizations Selector
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: exists (select 1 from OrganizationType ot where ot.id = e.organizationType.id and (ot.legalEntity=true or ot.businessUnit=true or ot.id='0')) AND e.ready=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Service Products
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.DESCRIPTION: This selector shows all the service products
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HELP: This selector shows all the service products

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Product
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.active='Y' and (cast(ad_org_isinnaturaltree(e.orgwarehouse, @AD_Org_Id@, @AD_Client_Id@) as string)='Y') and e.productPrice.priceListVersion.active='Y' and (cast(ad_org_isinnaturaltree(e.productPrice.organization.id, @AD_Org_Id@, @AD_Client_Id@) as string)='Y')
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: if (OB.getParameters().get('inpcCurrencyId') && (OB.getWindowId() == '207' || OB.getWindowId() == '94EAA455D2644E04AB25D93BE5157B6D')) { " e.productPrice.priceListVersion.priceList.currency.id = '" + OB.getParameters().get('inpcCurrencyId') + "'" } else if (OB.getParameters().get('inpcCurrencyId')) { " e.productPrice.priceListVersion.priceList.salesPriceList = " + OB.isSalesTransaction() + " AND e.productPrice.priceListVersion.priceList.currency.id = '" + OB.getParameters().get('inpcCurrencyId') + "'" }

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: StorageBin Selector without warehouse
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.warehouse.id IN (SELECT warehouse.id FROM OrganizationWarehouse o where o.organization.id=@inpadOrgId@ )

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Business Partner not filtered by default by customer/vendor
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: SELECT distinct bp.name as name,bp.id as bpid, bp.searchKey as value, bp.creditLimit - bp.creditUsed as creditAvailable, bp.creditUsed as creditUsed, COALESCE(contact.name, usercontact.name) as contactname, COALESCE(contact.id, usercontact.id) as contactid, bploc.name as locationname, bploc.id as locationid, bp.customer as customer, bp.vendor as vendor, bp.lifetimeRevenueToDate as income FROM BusinessPartner bp left join bp.businessPartnerLocationList bploc left join bploc.locationAddress loc left join bploc.aDUserList contact left join loc.region region left join bp.aDUserList usercontact with usercontact.partnerAddress.id is null where @additional_filters@ and bp.summaryLevel = false and bp.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Product Complete
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: "( (\'"+OB.getWindowId()+"\' in (\'800051\', \'800052\', \'800096\') and e.product.production = true and e.stocked = false) or (\'"+OB.getWindowId()+"\' in (\'800053\', \'FF808181323E504701323E57E08D0017\') and e.product.production = true) or (\'"+OB.getWindowId()+"\' in (\'170\') and e.product.stocked = true) or (\'"+OB.getWindowId()+"\' in (\'800092\') and e.product.purchase = true) or (\'"+OB.getWindowId()+"\' in (\'169\') and (e.warehouse.id is null or e.warehouse.id in (select ow.warehouse.id from OrganizationWarehouse ow where ow.organization.id = \'"+ OB.getParameters().get("inpadOrgId")+"\'))) or \'"+OB.getWindowId()+"\' not in (\'800051\', \'800052\', \'800053\', \'FF808181323E504701323E57E08D0017\', \'800096\',\'170\',\'800092\',\'169\'))"

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: UOM Selector
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.id not in (select p.uOM.id from Product p where p.id = @M_Product_ID@) and e.id not in (select a.uOM.id from ProductAUM a where a.product.id = @M_Product_ID@)

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Reservation
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.product.id = @inpmProductId@ AND e.rESStatus not in ('DR', 'CL') AND (e.storageBin IS NULL OR e.storageBin = (SELECT e FROM Locator e WHERE e.id = @M_Locator_ID@)) AND (e.warehouse IS NULL OR e.warehouse = (SELECT warehouse FROM Locator WHERE id = @M_Locator_ID@))

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Account Schema Selector
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: "EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OrganizationAcctSchema s WHERE s.accountingSchema.id = e.id AND AD_ISORGINCLUDED('"+OB.getParameters().get('Organization')+"', e.organization.id, @AD_CLIENT_ID@) <> -1)"

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Order for invoicing
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.salesTransaction = true and e.documentStatus NOT IN ('DR','IP') AND ((e.invoiceTerms = 'O' AND NOT EXISTS (select 1 from OrderLine where salesOrder.id = e.id and orderedQuantity <> deliveredQuantity) AND EXISTS (select 1 from OrderLine where salesOrder.id = e.id and orderedQuantity <> invoicedQuantity)) OR (e.invoiceTerms = 'D' AND EXISTS (select 1 from OrderLine where salesOrder.id = e.id and orderedQuantity <> invoicedQuantity and invoicedQuantity <> deliveredQuantity)) OR (e.invoiceTerms = 'I' AND EXISTS (select 1 from OrderLine where salesOrder.id = e.id and orderedQuantity <> invoicedQuantity)))

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Business Partner with contact and location
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: SELECT bp.name as name,bp.id as bpid, bp.searchKey as value, bp.creditLimit - bp.creditUsed as creditAvailable, bp.creditUsed as creditUsed, bp.customer as customer, bp.vendor as vendor, bp.businessPartnerCategory.name as category FROM BusinessPartner bp where @additional_filters@ and bp.summaryLevel = false and bp.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Payment Selector
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.status in ('RPR', 'PPM') and e.amount <>0 and exists ( select 1 from FinancialMgmtFinAccPaymentMethod as fapm join fapm.account as fa where fapm.paymentMethod = e.paymentMethod and fa.id = @FIN_Financial_Account_ID@ and (case when e.receipt = true then fapm.payinAllow else fapm.payoutAllow end) = true and fa.currency = e.account.currency) and not exists (select 1 from FIN_Finacc_Transaction as ft where e = ft.finPayment) and AD_ISORGINCLUDED(e.organization.id, @inpadOrgId@, e.client.id)<>-1

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Product Multiple
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: NOT EXISTS (SELECT pchv FROM ProductCharacteristicValue AS pchv WHERE pchv.characteristic.id = @M_Characteristic_ID@ AND pchv.product = e)

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Org_no_org_access
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select org.id as orgid, org.name as name, org.searchKey as value from Organization org where @additional_filters@

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Legal Organizations Selector
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: exists (select 1 from OrganizationType ot where ot = e.organizationType and ot.legalEntity = true) AND e.ready=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Element Value
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.active = true and exists (select 1 from FinancialMgmtAcctSchemaElement c where c.accountingSchema.id=@inpcAcctschemaId@ and c.accountingElement.id = e.accountingElement.id)

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Item Stockable Products
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.DESCRIPTION: This selector shows all the item stockable products
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HELP: This selector shows all the item stockable products
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.active='Y' AND e.isGeneric='N' AND e.productType='I' AND e.stocked='Y'

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: AUM Selector Filtered by Product
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: "e.id in (select p.uOM.id from Product p where p.id = '" + OB.getParameters().get('inpmProductId') + "') or e.id in (select a.uOM.id from ProductAUM a where a.product.id = '" + OB.getParameters().get('inpmProductId') + "')"

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: On Hand Locator
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: "((" + OB.isSalesTransaction() + " = true and e.warehouse.id in (select ow.warehouse.id from OrganizationWarehouse ow where ow.warehouse.id = e.warehouse.id and ow.active = true and ow.organization.id = \'" + OB.getParameters().get('inpadOrgId') + "\' )) or " + OB.isSalesTransaction() + " = false)"

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: ProductSimple
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: if (OB.getParameters().get('inpcCurrencyId')){ " pl.salesPriceList = " + OB.isSalesTransaction() + " AND c.id = '" + OB.getParameters().get('inpcCurrencyId') + "'" }
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.searchKey as searchKey, e.id as id, plv as priceListVersion, plv.name as priceListVersionName, c.id as currency, pp.priceLimit as priceLimit, e.name as productName, e.uOM as uOM, pp.standardPrice as standardPrice, pp.listPrice as netListPrice, pl.salesPriceList as salesPriceList, e.characteristicDescription as chDescription, gp.name as genericProduct from PricingProductPrice pp join pp.product e join pp.priceListVersion plv join plv.priceList pl left join pl.currency c left join e.genericProduct gp where e.isGeneric = 'N' and e.active = 'Y' and plv.active = 'Y' and @additional_filters@

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Business Partner with contact and location
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: SELECT distinct bp.name as name,bp.id as bpid, bp.searchKey as value, bp.creditLimit - bp.creditUsed as creditAvailable, bp.creditUsed as creditUsed, COALESCE(contact.name, usercontact.name) as contactname, COALESCE(contact.id, usercontact.id) as contactid, bploc.name as locationname, bploc.id as locationid, bp.customer as customer, bp.vendor as vendor, bp.lifetimeRevenueToDate as income FROM BusinessPartner bp left join bp.businessPartnerLocationList bploc with bploc.active=true left join bploc.locationAddress loc with loc.active = true left join bploc.aDUserList contact with contact.active=true left join loc.region region left join bp.aDUserList usercontact with usercontact.partnerAddress.id is null and usercontact.active=true where @additional_filters@ and bp.summaryLevel = false and bp.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Receipts
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.salesTransaction = false and e.documentStatus = 'CO' and exists (select 1 from MaterialMgmtMaterialTransaction t join t.goodsShipmentLine iol where iol.shipmentReceipt.id = e.id and iol.movementQuantity >= 0 and exists (select 1 from CostingRule r where r.validated = 'Y' and r.endingDate is null and (r.startingDate is null or r.startingDate <= t.transactionProcessDate)) and t.organization.id in (select ro.organization.id from ADRoleOrganization ro where ro.role.id = @#AD_Role_ID@))

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: On hand warehouse
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: "( (" + OB.isSalesTransaction() + " = true and w.id in (select ow.warehouse.id from OrganizationWarehouse ow where ow.warehouse.id = w.id and ow.active='Y' and ow.organization.id = \'" + OB.getParameters().get('inpadOrgId') + "\' )) or ((" + OB.isSalesTransaction() + " = false or \'"+OB.getWindowId()+"\' in (\'123271B9AD60469BAE8A924841456B63\'))))"
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select w.id as id, w.name as name from Warehouse w where @additional_filters@ and w.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Operative UOM Selector
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.id in (select p.uOM.id from Product p where p.id = @M_Product_ID@) or e.id in (select a.uOM.id from ProductAUM a where a.product.id = @M_Product_ID@)
